data.description: MOVE-IN-READY Tri-Level home in Chesterfield County.  This 3 Bedroom 2 FULL bathroom home received a make-over. As you drive up you will notice the circle driveway, half brick and vinyl siding home with updated windows. New paint (in every room), wall-to wall carpet and water proof plank vinyl flooring throughout the house; living room, bathrooms, laundry room, kitchen and dining room that has sliding glass doors to lead you out back to the “covered” patio deck. The spacious kitchen offers granite counter tops, stainless appliances: flat top stove, dishwasher, microwave and refrigerator. Take a few steps up to the second level to view the three bedrooms with ceiling fans in every room, walk-in closets and a balcony deck off the primary bedroom. Walk down a few steps from the first level to the family room with a “second” full bathroom, laundry room, living room with a wood fireplace to keep warm in the winter.  You can access the back yard from the basement or through the dining room area to enjoy the fenced in back yard (with a storage shed) and a covered deck overhang off the main deck for grilling out of the weather.  This is a great place call it your H.O.M.E
